name: Traveler
message: My lady, the task is done

name: Lady Liana
message: Good to hear that, so what does the people say?

name: Traveler
message: They need better conditions to live, and for that they need less taxes

name: Traveler
message: All they do is serve, but they are not compensated as they should

name: Lady Liana
message: I see... I will talk to the king about this, but I can't promise anything

name: Traveler
message: You need to try hard my lady, all this people is starving and sinking in taxes and taxes

name: Lady Liana
message: You know.. you should come with me to the king, I think he will listen to you

name: Traveler
message: Me? but Im just a traveler...

name: Lady Liana
message: And for that I think you will be heard, come with me

name: Lady Liana
message: Thank you for everything, we will talk to the king about this
